name: date
description: date and time

name: ticker symbol
description: ticker symbol for asset or index

name: best bid price
description: highest price that a buyer is willing to pay for a unit of the  asset

name: best ask price
description: lowest price that a seller is willing to sell a unit of the  asset

name: bid size
description: The quantity/size of the highest price bid

name: ask size
description: The quantity/size of the lowest price ask

name: trade size
description: number of units of asset traded

name: trade price
description: price of asset in units of quote currency

name: trade side
description: buy or sell, side taking liquidity

name: open price
description: open price of OHLC bar

name: high price
description: high price of OHLC bar

name: low price
description: low price of OHLC bar

name: close price
description: close price of OHLC bar

name: volume
description: number of units of asset traded within time interval

name: volume-weighted avg price
description: average volume-weighted price of quote asset within time interval

name: open interest
description: number of outstanding futures contracts that are open and have yet to be settled

name: funding rate
description: interest rate for holding derivative contract within time interval

name: market capitalization
description: usd value of circulating supply

name: active addresses
description: number of unique addresses that were active in the network, as a sender or receiver, within time interval

name: new addresses
description: number of new unique addresses that were created in the network , within time interval

name: active addresses sent
description: number of unique addresses that were active in the network, as a sender, within time interval

name: active addresses received
description: number of unique addresses that were active in the network, as a receiver, within time interval

name: total address count
description: number of unique addresses in the network  at the end of the period

name: addresses with positive balance
description: number of unique addresses  with positive balance in the network at the end of the period

name: addresses with zero balance count
description: number of unique addresses  with zero balance in the network at the end of the period

name: transactions
description: number of transactions in the network within time interval

name: transactions rate
description: number of transactions per second

name: transaction size
description: mean size of transactions within time interval

name: mean transaction fee
description: mean fee per transaction within time interval

name: mean transaction fee in usd
description: mean fee per transaction within time interval, in usd

name: transfers value
description: number of units of asset transferred in the network within time interval

name: mean transfers value
description: mean transfer value in the network within time interval

name: velocity
description: ratio of transfer value over the past year over circulating supply at the end of the period

name: transactions larger than 100k usd count
description: number of transactions in the network larger than 100k usd within time interval

name: total transactions count
description: number of transactions in the network at the end of the period

name: unspent transaction outputs
description: total transaction output that can be used as input in a new transaction

name: unspent transaction outputs created
description: number of created unspent transaction outputs

name: spent transaction outputs
description: number of spent transaction outputs

name: newly created asset units utxo
description: numbrer of assets units in newly created UTXOs

name: asset units in spent transaction outputs
description: numbrer of assets units in spent transaction outputs

name: mean newly created asset units utxo
description: mean numbrer of assets units in newly created UTXOs

name: mean asset units in spent transaction outputs
description: mean numbrer of assets units in spent transaction outputs

name: hash rate
description: mean number of hashes per second produced by the miners in the network within time interval

name: difficulty of last block
description: number of hashes required to mine the last block within time interval

name: mean difficulty of a block
description: mean number of hashes required to mine a block within time interval

name: block height
description: number of blocks created and included in the main blockchain since the genesis block

name: mean block size
description: mean size of blocks created within time interval

name: mean block time
description: mean time for block to be created within time interval

name: miner revenue
description: total miner revenue, fees plus newly minted coins within time interval

name: miner revenue in usd
description: total miner revenue, fees plus newly minted coins within time interval, in usd

name: miner revenue
description: miner revenue dervied from fees within time interval

name: miner revenue from fees
description: miner revenue dervied from fees within time interval, in usd

name: miner revenue from block rewards
description: miner revenue dervied from block rewards within time interval

name: total miner revenue in usd
description: total miner revenue, fees plus newly minted coins in usd at the end of the period

name: circulating supply
description: total number of asset units issued/created on the ledger at the end of the period

name: free float supply
description: total number of asset units issued/created on the ledger at the end of the period, excluding tokens held closely by company insiders, controlling investors and long term strategic holders

name: issuance
description: number of new asset units issues within time interval

name: pecent of supply active in the past year
description: percentage of current supply that has been active in the trailing 1 year up to the end of the period

name: stocks-to-flow ratio
description: ratio of the circulating supply to the newly issued asset units within time interval, or the inverse of the issuance rate.

name: spent output price ratio
description: ratio of the sum of spent value over the sum of creation value of all spent and created outputs for that interval

name: assets under management
description: total assets under fund's management

name: fund flows
description: inflows/outflows into fund

name: fund asset holdings
description: fund's asset holdings
